# Regression: legacy edgecell pwr/gnd fixture lines are ordinary boundary I/O.
#
# The line below must drive only the inward-facing Sinew value on the left edge.
# It must not rewrite the boundary cell body, parent pointer, or config state.

grid 16 16

frame 1
edgecell left 4 pwr parent right

expect frame 1 cell 0 4 fields orientation=2 mode=0 parent=0 right=1 conf=1 full=0 wp=0
expect frame 1 edge left sr 4 1
